statements.sql: select `project_teams`.*, `projects`.*, CONCAT(customers.company_name, ' - ', customers.last_name, ' ', customers.first_name) AS customer_info, `phases`.`phase_name_eng` from `projects` inner join `contracts` on `contracts`.`contract_id` = `projects`.`contract_id` inner join `customers` on `customers`.`customer_id` = `contracts`.`customer_id` inner join `phases` on `phases`.`phase_id` = `projects`.`phase_id` inner join `project_teams` on `project_teams`.`project_id` = `projects`.`project_id` order by `project_teams`.`project_id` asc
select * from `team_details` inner join `employees` on `employees`.`employee_id` = `team_details`.`employee_id` where `team_id` = 67 order by `team_permission` asc

SELECT
employees.*, accounts.*,team_details.team_permission as team_permission,
CASE
WHEN team_details.employee_id IS NOT NULL THEN 1
ELSE 0
END AS isAtTeam
FROM
employees
JOIN
accounts ON accounts.employee_id = employees.employee_id
LEFT JOIN
team_details ON team_details.employee_id = employees.employee_id AND team_details.team_id = 67
